{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"attributeName","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/attributeName","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n\n<p>该属性标识了在一个动画动作环节中，父元素的需要被改变的属性名。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td>动画属性目标属性</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td>&lt;attributeName&gt;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可变性</th>\n   <td>No</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/animate.html#AttributeNameAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下面的示例使用了 y 作为<code>attributeName</code>，通过改变一个矩形在 Y 轴上的位置来变动这个矩形。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token prolog\">&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\"?&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>250<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>250<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">viewPort</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0 0 250 250<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">version</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1.1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2000/svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>rect</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">x</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>50<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">y</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>50<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>animate</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">attributeType</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>XML<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token attr-name\">attributeName</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>y<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token attr-name\">from</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">to</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>50<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token attr-name\">dur</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>5s<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>rect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下列元素可以使用<code>attributeName</code>属性：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/animate\"><code>&lt;animate&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/animate\"><code>&lt;animateColor&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/animateTransform\"><code>&lt;animateTransform&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/set\"><code>&lt;set&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"attributeName","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"attributeName","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/attributename","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/attributename/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/attributeName","title":"attributeName"}],"pageTitle":"attributeName - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}